\f1\b0 \uc0\u8232 Find one recent long-form article (essay, reported feature, or serious review\'97not a news brief) that would plausibly interest a reader with advanced training in economics and the humanities.\

\f0\b Source strategy:
\f1\b0 \uc0\u8232 Select the article from one of three categories, aiming for balance over time:\u8232 \'96 Italian-language publications\u8232 \'96 English-language publications\u8232 \'96 Non-Anglophone, non-Italian publications (translation acceptable or encouraged)\

\f0\b Preferred outlets include (not exhaustive):
\f1\b0 \uc0\u8232 \'96 
\f2\i Italian:
\f1\i0  Il Post, Internazionale, Limes, Domani, il Mulino, Doppiozero\uc0\u8232 \'96 
\f2\i English:
